  "texts": [
    "District Judge Anthony A. Alaimo discusses the potential scope of impact outside of traditional economic topics, but to areas of judicial discretion more broadly:",
    "While we are circumscribed by the parameters of existing statutes, regulations and case law, there is a wide area of decision entrusted to us where the result can go either way, depending on how we view the evidence.",
    "That area is called judicial discretion.\"",
    "This is the area that is most aected by these seminars on economics conducted under Dr. Manne's direction.",
    "I have attended his seminars during the past ten years and am eager to testify to their value."
  ],
